summary: Ingegerd M. Keith (formerly Burgaz) was born June 14, 1941 in Stockholm, Sweden. He is a research associate at the University of Wisconsin-Madi son. His research interests include pulmonary neuroendocrine cell dynamics and the regulation of circulation.
